data.description: Here is your slice of the Mt Baker with this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on a large double lot .350 Acres, and has green belt around all sides, Laminate throughout the house, ceramic tile in bathrooms. Beautiful kitchen with white cabinets, quartz countertops and a large pantry. 20x14 covered deck just steps out your back for relaxing or entertaining, opening up to a huge FENCED back yard, great for play and pets. Master bedroom features a large walk-in closet with double French doors to the bathroom, double sink, and a huge soaker tub. All appliances stay! Wired for generator.
